Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.34,0:00:03.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Waiting gets us nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.76,0:00:05.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take a step forward into the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a deduction and love countdown!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.85,0:00:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The words "red, white and yellow" written in a diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.64,0:00:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are an important hint to solving the riddle of a case.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:12.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Perceiving the one and only truth...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:13.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:15.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.18,0:02:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.69,0:02:14.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? There's nothing in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So there are zero requests today as well, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:19.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How boring!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.28,0:02:19.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.20,0:02:22.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means it's good that things are peaceful, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.99,0:02:23.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.66,0:02:30.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who would be calling me at this time?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.88,0:02:32.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's weird though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:33.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the same as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.88,0:02:34.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hi, Cool Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.55,0:02:40.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your classes just got finished, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.26,0:02:41.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:43.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.14,0:02:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I called your cellphone several times but it wouldn't connect.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.60,0:02:47.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:51.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After that "Shiranpuri" case, my cellphone broke\Ndown for good and I had to buy a replacement.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.31,0:02:55.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With all that's happened, I decided to\Nstart anew and got a new number also.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.90,0:03:01.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, as appropriate, I informed that girl who's\Ninfiltrating the Organization about the new number.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.66,0:03:02.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.20,0:03:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mizunashi Rena{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.49,0:03:05.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.28,0:03:07.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then I got a call from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:12.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems they were off guard for a bit, so it was a fairly short call, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.92,0:03:14.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She was able to tell me this quite clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:18.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Organization has activated a new member.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.46,0:03:23.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,An agent who is frighteningly skilled at intelligence\Ngathering as well as observation and discernment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.18,0:03:24.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Codename:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:26.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bourbon!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.60,0:03:27.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:31.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all she could tell me in our short conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.77,0:03:38.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Judging from her harsh tone, that agent is pretty sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.98,0:03:41.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And most likely their target is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:45.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That girl with the brown-dyed hair,\Nknown to the Organization as Sherry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.37,0:03:47.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's wait and see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I expect so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.66,0:03:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As far as the FBI is concerned, we'd like to assign a bodyguard to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, if we do that now, we would be in danger of\Nletting them know her whereabouts instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.92,0:04:03.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the short term, it seems it'd be better to\Navoid that risk and put our trust in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, be vigilant and protect her closely for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.89,0:04:11.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if anything happens, be sure and contact us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.90,0:04:18.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Codename...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.28,0:04:20.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bourbon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what should we do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.82,0:04:26.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, with this rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.45,0:04:28.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How about a game at the Professor's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.24,0:04:31.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's go, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.20,0:04:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:36.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder what you're going to discuss\Nwith the Professor when you see him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mr. Great Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.50,0:04:39.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That phone call just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.17,0:04:42.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was from Jodie{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-sensei{\r} and the FBI, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:44.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was nothing for you to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.01,0:04:51.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"For me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're hiding something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, I mean it's not like another case occurred or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:56.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a case!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.06,0:05:00.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A case between Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and Ai{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.03,0:05:02.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, behind them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.20,0:05:13.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, to summarize your story, first year\Nstudent from class A, Sugiura Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:22.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your father is the landlord of a small apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.92,0:05:25.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That apartment building has three residents.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.30,0:05:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And one of those three has been behaving suspiciously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.89,0:05:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you want us Detective Boys\Nto find out what he's been doing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:35.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.35,0:05:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, let's stay over at this guy's place\Ntonight and we can all keep watch on that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that sounds good. Tomorrow is Saturday, so there's no school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:46.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.61,0:05:48.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, today is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.78,0:05:50.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because tonight's...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.28,0:05:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The night I play Othello with my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:06:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why earlier you put your request in the shoe\Nbox after we had all left for home, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.25,0:06:03.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you wouldn't miss your chance to play with your father today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:04.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:10.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, in that case, we wouldn't have gotten\Nyour letter until next week Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.80,0:06:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so? What kind of suspicious things is that person doing at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:18.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for that, come over and stay at my house tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.48,0:06:21.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It would be better if you could see for yourself, Kuroshi—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah! If it's all right, why don't you come during the day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.61,0:06:31.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to show you my room and the inside of the apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.53,0:06:34.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we all go at noon tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.08,0:06:34.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:40.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My house is in the apartment building called\N"Mokubasou" at Beika City, 2nd district, number 23.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.58,0:06:42.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll see you tomorrow, Kuroshi—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.71,0:06:43.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.00,0:06:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:46.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.72,0:06:52.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How come it's just Conan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:54.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what's that "Kuroshi" thing about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was just trying to say "yoroshiku" (thanks).
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:03.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Mokubasou" at Beika City, 2nd district, number 23...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:06.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? Do you recognize it? That apartment building?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:07.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think it's somewhere near the Professor's house though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:11.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I pass in front of that apartment building a lot on my way home.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's old and small, but it's a nice agreeable building.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.10,0:07:37.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Beika City...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:39.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,2nd district...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Number 23...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Mokubasou."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is it, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.37,0:08:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been completely burned down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:01.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.96,0:08:04.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, I did hear the sounds of sirens during the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:07.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But what about that boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.51,0:08:11.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What happened to Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.97,0:08:13.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe he was caught in the fire and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.51,0:08:15.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.76,0:08:18.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that boy Kaito is safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:23.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He got a few burns, but he was rescued by one of the firemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.39,0:08:25.10,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yuminaga\NPolice HQ Division One Investigations\NChief Arson Investigator
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:25.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's asleep at the hospital now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.77,0:08:27.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.61,0:08:28.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.48,0:08:30.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yuminaga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.90,0:08:33.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh! You're the boy from Mouri's place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.70,0:08:35.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen you since that "Red Horse" case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.32,0:08:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.45,0:08:40.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That happened a while ago when Hattori Heiji had come to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.08,0:08:45.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The person in charge of that murder/arson\Ncase was this guy, Inspector Yuminaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:50.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, did anyone die in this fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.09,0:08:53.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Happily, there were no fatalities.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.42,0:08:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s father was badly burned and is in the ICU now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:05.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the rest of that boy's family and the other residents of this\Napartment building were all able to get away during the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.56,0:09:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The boy's mother happened to be away on a trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.73,0:09:13.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I called her at her hotel earlier, she was\Nastonished and said she was coming back immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.61,0:09:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As for the three other residents, all three of them\Nhappened to be out at around the time of the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:22.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems they didn't come back until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:23.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:25.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't the fire happen in the middle of the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.16,0:09:26.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.37,0:09:29.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Around 2:30 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.54,0:09:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, the three of them aren't kids, so there's nothing suspicious\Nabout them going out in the evening and staying out all night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.84,0:09:39.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's got to be one of those three who set the fire, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.68,0:09:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.89,0:09:46.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yesterday Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} told us that one of those three\Npeople was doing suspicious things at night!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:50.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But when we came here to investigate,\Nwe found that this had happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.65,0:09:53.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yuminaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:56.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We found this in the remains of the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:09:58.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:01.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This must be Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:11.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's see. The last page says July 4th. That's yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The weather has been bad since this morning. I have to get up\Nearly or I'll miss school, but I bet the red guy can sleep in late."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.72,0:10:23.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What does this "red guy" mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:28.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"When I got back from school, I fell down in the entryway."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I'm glad the white guy was just coming out."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.94,0:10:37.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Tonight the red guy and the white guy\Nand the yellow guy are all going out."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.65,0:10:46.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My dad and I are alone together. I want to play some more but the\Ndetective club is coming tomorrow, so I should go to bed early."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.45,0:10:49.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Who is it? Someone came home in the middle of the night."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:52.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"He's arguing with my father."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.29,0:10:54.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It's the yellow guy."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.88,0:10:58.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"I wonder if my dad found out about the suspicious things he's doing."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"It's scary, so I'll cover my ears and go to bed. When\NI wake up I'll have to tell Edogawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} about this."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:08.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's obvious that the yellow guy set the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.81,0:11:09.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector Yuminaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.27,0:11:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What kind of people are those three residents?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.81,0:11:13.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:17.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, sorry about this, but could you\Nbring those three over here for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.46,0:11:38.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A glare that impales its prey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:46.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pressure that's eating into my guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.14,0:11:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.18,0:11:51.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.60,0:11:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Somewhere nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.81,0:11:56.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A member of the Organization!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.16,0:12:12.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're here...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:14.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:16.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A member of the Organization...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:18.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:20.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could they be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:22.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no time to think.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've got to get away from here quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:29.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or else everyone will...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It went away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.31,0:12:36.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.52,0:12:38.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.61,0:12:39.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:41.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.03,0:12:45.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, would you mind answering a\Nfew more questions from my officers?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:46.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This way, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.16,0:12:50.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:54.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which one of those three was the suspicious person?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.92,0:12:56.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.37,0:12:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We came to see Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} to ask him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:02.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? Couldn't you have mentioned that earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.71,0:13:03.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:05.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What do those three people do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.68,0:13:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From the right:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.18,0:13:12.56,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Hosoi Ryuuhei (25)\NCarpenter
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:12.56,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The one with the band-aid is a carpenter, Hosoi Ryuuhei{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.77,0:13:17.60,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,The one with the glasses is a graduate student, Okiya Subaru{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.02,0:13:17.60,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)} Okiya Subaru (27)\NGraduate Student
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.90,0:13:22.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,And the heavy one is a part-time worker, Makabe Ginya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.02,0:13:22.57,Character Card,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,0)}Makabe Ginya (29)\NPart-Timer
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:26.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I suppose one of those three is the yellow guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:30.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, what's that? The "yellow guy"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:31.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:32.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Read this for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.58,0:13:36.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a diary that the landlord's son wrote.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.25,0:13:39.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to that, for some reason, on the\Nday before the fire it seems Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:46.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Asked these kids to investigate one of the\Nresidents who was behaving questionably.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:47.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're not just kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:49.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We're the highly-respected...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.85,0:13:51.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Detective Boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.18,0:13:55.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, he referred to them that way in his diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.48,0:13:59.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm inclined to think he's using colors to stand\Nfor the residents of this apartment building.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to what's written here, it seems certain that whichever\Nresident is the "yellow guy" is the culprit, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.11,0:14:12.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, however, we don't know which of them is the "yellow guy".
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.62,0:14:15.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of the three have a color in their names.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.08,0:14:18.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nobody is wearing yellow clothing either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.92,0:14:22.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Their jobs are carpenter, student, and temp.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.29,0:14:25.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing there that's associated with a color.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:27.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Red, white, and yellow?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.13,0:14:29.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's like the colors of flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's a black guy though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A black person?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, that dark-skinned man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:42.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, if it's the color of their skin, then that\Nguy with the glasses is white, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.73,0:14:43.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's ask them a bit more detailed\Nquestions and see what we find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.78,0:14:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Such as who is the certain "yellow" person in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:55.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.49,0:14:57.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to say the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.79,0:14:58.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On the night of the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.50,0:15:03.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was out drinking with my boss and my\Nsuperiors from the carpentry trade.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.46,0:15:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But earlier when we were confirming that, it seems\Nyou left sometime after 1 o'clock in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:10.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.34,0:15:14.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I haven't been drinking in a long time, so I got really drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.18,0:15:20.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To try to sober up, I went off by myself and\Nlaid down on a bench and fell asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.69,0:15:22.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And so, when I came to, it was already morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.40,0:15:26.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then at the time of the fire, around 2:30 in the morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:29.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That means there was nobody with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:31.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:33.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, why do you have that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.74,0:15:36.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That band-aid on your face. Did you get in a fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.24,0:15:38.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's with this kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's OK, just answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:44.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got hit by a board while I was working.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.58,0:15:46.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm still a beginner, so I keep getting injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.71,0:15:47.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.75,0:15:48.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These are all from work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:51.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, what's your favorite color?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:52.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Color?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:54.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The blue of the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.43,0:15:57.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's cause I like to go surfing occasionally.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was driving by myself that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:07.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do that frequently whenever I start going crazy\Ntrying to prepare my thesis for my professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:09.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whereabouts did you go driving?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.24,0:16:12.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I drove down that tree-lined street by the Teimuzu River.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.15,0:16:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I'm looking at the greenery, my heart\Nfeels at ease, so I end up along there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:23.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I water the plants in the garden at\Nthis apartment building every day too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:27.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's because the landlord doesn't seem\Nvery interested in maintaining the garden.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.38,0:16:31.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, then your favorite color is green or something then?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.01,0:16:32.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:35.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you force me to pick one...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.97,0:16:36.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be black.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It covers up the things inside of me\Nthat I don't want to be know about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:44.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, for the same reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Black is the color I hate too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.11,0:16:52.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Last night I went to see a movie in Haido City.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.94,0:16:56.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was an all-night showing from\N10PM at night until 5AM in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:16:58.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a triple feature from the "Monster Gomera" series.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.28,0:17:00.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Were you alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.37,0:17:01.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.45,0:17:05.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My net friend was supposed to go with\Nme, but he suddenly couldn't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's a "net friend"?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:10.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, as a side-line, I work as a day trader.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:15.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have some friends who exchange information\Nwith me about that on the internet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.47,0:17:18.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A day trader? So you deal with stocks and such?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:23.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just sort of a hobby, so I only make\Na ridiculously small amount of profit from it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.35,0:17:28.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your only a part-time worker, but you earn enough\Nto cover your living expenses from that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.15,0:17:28.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:31.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I'm registered with a temp agency for daily work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.73,0:17:32.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Say, about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:35.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you do public construction work?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.28,0:17:40.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,See, there's a lot of mud under your finger nails.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.20,0:17:46.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's mud from the time I played a survival game a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's because I was running around in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.79,0:17:53.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since they got covered in that bright color\Nfrom paint gun shells, I ruined my clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:59.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then your favorite color is the color that camouflage\Nclothing is usually made from, navy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:00.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.55,0:18:03.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's navy green.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:06.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:09.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do our favorite colors have something to do with the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you never know.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.86,0:18:14.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tsuburaya{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could you help me with a little something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:18.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.91,0:18:20.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stay like that and walk backwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.32,0:18:22.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:24.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Walk backwards?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:26.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is there something behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:27.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.12,0:18:30.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You need to keep looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.33,0:18:31.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:33.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:36.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.80,0:18:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's definitely one of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.22,0:18:42.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one I sensed that pressure from earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.51,0:18:43.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A member of the Organization.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.68,0:18:47.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to figure out who it is right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.35,0:18:49.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.19,0:18:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or else these kids will get mixed up in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Haibara{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, this hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.24,0:18:57.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:58.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:00.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.36,0:19:01.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.87,0:19:04.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I only scraped a little skin off my elbow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.54,0:19:05.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.37,0:19:08.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:09.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This band-aid.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.91,0:19:11.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:12.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:13.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.29,0:19:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My boss told me that since I keep getting\Ninjured I should always carry some.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.89,0:19:27.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we assume it doesn't mean their favorite color,\Nwhat does it mean? This "yellow guy".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.22,0:19:29.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, Inspector.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.77,0:19:33.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't it dangerous to keep on concentrating on a kid's diary like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.40,0:19:36.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It might possibly just be an imaginary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.61,0:19:37.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:39.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He told us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.74,0:19:42.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There was a guy who was doing suspicious things at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.70,0:19:46.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really don't think it sounded like he made it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.16,0:19:46.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.66,0:19:49.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Moreover, whenever you police...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:51.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a child who's done something bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.87,0:19:55.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you start by asking the adults around him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If they know what kind of child he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.46,0:19:59.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't the converse true also?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:08.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if he's a child, Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} has observed the residents\Nclosely, even going so far as to give them nicknames.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.14,0:20:11.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Adventure of the Copper Beeches, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.35,0:20:14.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,During the case of the Adventure of the Copper Beeches...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:17.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was one of the lines that Holmes said to Dr. Watson.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:26.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"My dear Watson, you as a medical man are continually gaining\Nlight as to the tendencies of a child by the study of the parents."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:30.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Don't you see that the converse is equally valid."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.91,0:20:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.50,0:20:36.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You like Holmes too?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.71,0:20:37.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I used to have all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.92,0:20:41.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But they've all burned up now, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.67,0:20:44.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, speaking of Holmes...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.84,0:20:47.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He wouldn't have ignored this diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.68,0:20:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.26,0:20:51.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could I look at that diary?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.23,0:20:53.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.56,0:20:56.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.48,0:20:56.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:58.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have you found something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.98,0:20:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.23,0:21:01.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They were in the area near Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.28,0:21:03.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A pile of mini-cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.45,0:21:05.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mini-cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.57,0:21:09.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not strange for there to be some miniature cars in a child's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:12.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, there were quite a number.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Easily more than 100 of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.21,0:21:15.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:16.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.87,0:21:17.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.13,0:21:19.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.38,0:21:20.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look. Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.71,0:21:24.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The characters for "Edogawa" have been erased and\Nrewritten several times. The paper's even gotten a bit dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.34,0:21:27.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could he have been trying to write it in kanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.97,0:21:31.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, you can faintly see what looks like katakana underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be "Kuroshi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.77,0:21:35.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuroshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:36.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kuroshiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:40.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Earlier when I called the hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.36,0:21:42.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s mother said something.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.78,0:21:49.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"The really smart boy who solved a case that happened at\Nschool instantly is coming over to our house tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:53.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} seemed really happy when he told her that over the phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.37,0:21:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said he was called Kuroshiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:59.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then when Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} said "Kuroshi" yesterday...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.92,0:22:02.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was talking about Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.17,0:22:04.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why would he call him "Kuroshiro"?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:06.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.63,0:22:09.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess we'll have to wait until Kaito{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} gets better...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:11.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And ask him in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.68,0:22:12.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:14.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That won't be necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:20.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shall I be Kuroshiro{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.86,0:22:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And make plain what's black and white right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.99,0:22:27.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you which one among them is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:31.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The yellow arsonist.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:02.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The three of you said...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.21,0:24:04.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You'd gone out the night of the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.38,0:24:06.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And returned home in the morning, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.34,0:24:10.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If that's so, then somebody must be lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.88,0:24:14.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Which of these three people is the yellow arsonist?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.76,0:24:16.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already know who.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:17.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wh-What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:19.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh! Over there now is...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.31,0:24:21.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.39,0:24:23.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shin'ichi came home?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.17,0:24:48.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.54,0:24:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mini-car
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.00,0:24:51.96,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,A dish made from the skin of pigs' ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.00,0:24:51.96,Signs,,0,0,0,,mimi no kawa (ear skin) is a pun on mini-car
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.01,0:24:52.97,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,That's mimigaa.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.01,0:24:52.97,Signs,,0,0,0,,Okinawa cuisine
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.01,0:24:54.38,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Is that for your father?
